## Architecture overview

```
Browser
  └── Gateway :3000                          (single origin, JWT validation via JWKS)
        ├── /                → Shell :3001   (login / register / auth redirect)
        ├── /auth/*          → Auth Service :4001   (RS256 JWT, JWKS, refresh rotation)
        ├── /mfe/diary/*     → Diary Web :4280      (Next.js MFE, BlockNote editor)
        ├── /mfe/settings/*  → Settings Web :4380   (Next.js settings MFE)
        ├── /mfe/tasks/*     → Task Manager Web :4480 (Next.js MFE)
        ├── /diary/*         → Diary API :4281      (NestJS, Prisma, service token auth)
        ├── /settings/*      → Settings API :4381   (NestJS, Prisma, service token auth)
        └── /tasks/*         → Task Manager API :4481 (NestJS, Prisma, service token auth)

Background:
  Diary Worker  → NATS JetStream :42220  (outbox publisher for DIARY_EVENTS)
  LLM Service   → subscribes to DIARY_EVENTS (durable `llm-service`) → Ollama on host :11434
  Task Manager  → NATS JetStream :42221  (reserved for future TASK_MANAGER_EVENTS publisher)
```

Auth flow summary: `Shell` collects credentials → `Auth Service` issues RS256 JWT → JWT passed via hash fragment to `Diary Web` → `Gateway` validates JWT via JWKS on every subsequent request.
